<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935C8E01F6B6FC8DFAF3FCF2" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[1163,1314,799,825]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
